debrief.itemText: Please answer the following questions about your experience. Click and drag the red scrollbar to move down. Do not leave any box blank. Type ‘no’ or ‘n/a’ if you don’t have a response.
Briefly describe what you were asked to do in this experiment?
debrief.response: I was asked to pick a shape and was rewarded with points. I was then asked to decide which numbers/letters fit in a certain range, then asked to correctly click a key. Next i was asked to switch between the two tasks and was then shown the shape before the problem, and was rewarded points.
